<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-277] Callout Mediator contais hardcoded path to a samples config file</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-277</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in the init function of  org.apache.synapse.mediators.builtin.CalloutMediator&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;is a hardcoded path to a samples config file, i.e.:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;                ConfigurationContextFactory.createConfigurationContextFromFileSystem(&lt;br/&gt;
                    &quot;./samples/axis2Client/client_repo&quot;, &quot;./samples/axis2Client/client_repo/conf/axis2.xml&quot;);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This introduces a unwanted dependancy on sample code/config, perhaps the config, should be moved inside the &apos;core&apos; .&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>n/a, its in the source</environment>
