                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12592765" author="ruwan" created="Mon, 28 Apr 2008 08:33:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This can be easily fixed by exposing these values as callout parameters.... &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12593175" author="ruwan" created="Tue, 29 Apr 2008 23:48:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed on the SVN trunk. Now the client repo and the axis2.xml can be configured using the callout mediator configuration itself. You can add the following element to configure these properties;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;configuration axis2xml=&quot;string&quot; repository=&quot;string&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;but these are optional and if not provided, will be taken the values hardcoded earlier as defualt values, keeping the backward compatibility as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
